@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Raydar";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!-- Page-specific stylesheet -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/index.css" asp-append-version="true" />

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to Raydar</h1>
    <p>Developed by four passionate Computer Engineering students at UiA, Raydar is your SPF & UV tracking companion.</p>
    <div class="preview">
        <img src="~/images/preview1.png" alt="App Preview" class="img-fluid rounded mx-auto d-block" />
    </div>
    <div class="download-btn">
        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.raydar.app" target="_blank">
            <img src="~/images/playstore.png" alt="Get it on Google Play" />
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="features container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Morning UV Forecast</h2>
            <p>Each morning, Raydar tells you the day's UV index, helping you choose the correct SPF.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>SPF Recommendations</h2>
            <p>Based on the UV forecast, Raydar suggests the ideal SPF level to keep you protected.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Sunscreen Timer</h2>
            <p>Set reminders to reapply sunscreen at optimal intervals so you stay safe all day long.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Favorite Locations</h2>
            <p>Save multiple locations to quickly check UV forecasts wherever you go.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<hr class="section-divider">
<div class="theory container mt-5 py-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Why Raydar Matters</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center mb-5">
        UV rays are invisible, but their effects aren’t. Overexposure to ultraviolet radiation silently damages your skin — increasing the risk of premature aging, sunburn, and skin cancer. 
        Sunscreen helps, but only if it’s the right type, applied correctly, and reapplied on time.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h4>Understanding UV</h4>
            <p>
                The sun emits UVA and UVB rays. UVA penetrates deep, accelerating aging, while UVB causes sunburn and directly damages skin cells. Both increase the risk of skin cancer.
                Yet most people underestimate daily exposure — even on cloudy days or in winter.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h4>The Role of SPF</h4>
            <p>
                SPF isn't one-size-fits-all. Raydar helps you pick the right protection, and reminds you to reapply sunscreen at the optimal time — before it wears off.
                Our goal? Make skin safety second nature, not an afterthought.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
